          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to add new records to the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "BillingPeriod",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table within the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Preload",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema. It calculates and inserts billing periods for a new fiscal year based on the existing data in the table. The procedure generates 12 new billing periods, corresponding to each month of the fiscal year, and assigns them a budget billing period and a billing period value. The procedure also logs the creation date and the user who performed the action."
        }
